    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>La Furia de las Trenzas</strong></i> is a <strong>survivor-like roguelike</strong> where you'll face <strong>relentless hordes of British soldiers</strong> trying to capture <strong>Buenos Aires</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recruit</strong> your <strong>platoon of soldiers</strong> with special abilities and <strong>defend the town square!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/73907ab5e97f43de9891f27f3e6dcdb7.poster.avif?t=1760670049\" width=634 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/73907ab5e97f43de9891f27f3e6dcdb7.webm?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/73907ab5e97f43de9891f27f3e6dcdb7.mp4?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recruit</strong> soldiers belonging to different <strong>historical regiments</strong>, including <strong>Patricios</strong>, <strong>Arribeños</strong>, <strong>Correntinos</strong>, <strong>Morenos</strong>, <strong>Húsares</strong> and more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/1a4cbdc5ce459ba73207fba5ac131edc.poster.avif?t=1760670049\" width=634 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/1a4cbdc5ce459ba73207fba5ac131edc.webm?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/1a4cbdc5ce459ba73207fba5ac131edc.mp4?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn the support</strong> of the townsfolk of Buenos Aires through <strong>special events</strong> that turn the tide of battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/e34de2700b81d5b446c7fea4bf4d8167.poster.avif?t=1760670049\" width=634 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/e34de2700b81d5b446c7fea4bf4d8167.webm?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/e34de2700b81d5b446c7fea4bf4d8167.mp4?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the local militia</strong> alongside heroes like <strong>Santiago de Liniers</strong> and <strong>Manuela Pedraza!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/2a171efa1d19823787c2929bbe85db7a.poster.avif?t=1760670049\" width=634 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/2a171efa1d19823787c2929bbe85db7a.webm?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217730/extras/2a171efa1d19823787c2929bbe85db7a.mp4?t=1760670049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face powerful British units</strong> such as<strong> </strong>the <strong>Highlanders Regiment</strong>, the <strong>Rifle Battalion</strong>, the <strong>Royal Marines</strong> and the omnipresent <strong>Redcoats!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with <strong>keyboard</strong>, <strong>mouse</strong> or <strong>gamepad!</strong></p></li></ul>",
